Params: {2: 'Sophia', 3: "Didn't Aston tell you to stay put?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Changyu', 3: 'That thing... is trouble... Need to fight... Or else Corrupted will flood the carriages...', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Sophia', 3: '...Good job for holding it off for so long.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Changyu', 3: "...Never thought we'd be protected by someone from Babylonia.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Sophia', 3: "You've suffered severe damages, so speak less and try to hang on.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Changyu', 3: 'Heh... Are they here for the weakened prey that is me?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Changyu', 3: "Don't worry... I'm not that damaged yet... I can still fend for myself.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Sophia', 3: "Don't push yourself so much, I'll take care of them.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sophia', 3: 'While you, on the other hand, rest.', 4: '1'}
